1
00:01:20,990 --> 00:01:26,700
[A Splendid Match]

2
00:01:27,460 --> 00:01:29,789
[Episode 15]

3
00:01:29,970 --> 00:01:39,440
[Memorial]

4
00:01:46,120 --> 00:01:47,120
My mother

5
00:01:48,090 --> 00:01:49,560
asked me to pass along a few words

6
00:01:49,560 --> 00:01:50,759
to Miss Gu.

7
00:01:53,680 --> 00:01:54,310
Rong,

8
00:01:55,200 --> 00:01:55,920
Lan,

9
00:01:56,440 --> 00:01:59,759
[Memorial]

10
00:01:56,509 --> 00:01:57,380
come with me.

11
00:02:12,750 --> 00:02:13,710
Are you alright?

12
00:02:14,750 --> 00:02:15,800
I'm fine.

13
00:02:19,150 --> 00:02:20,810
I'm sorry your mother is gone.

14
00:02:21,000 --> 00:02:22,030
Miss Gu, I hope you

15
00:02:22,750 --> 00:02:24,079
accept my condolences,

16
00:02:25,120 --> 00:02:26,400
and take care of yourself.

17
00:02:26,400 --> 00:02:28,930
That is the best way
to honor your late mother.

18
00:02:30,870 --> 00:02:31,630
I know.

19
00:02:34,079 --> 00:02:36,000
I heard the Old Madam came as well.

20
00:02:39,000 --> 00:02:40,329
She arrived yesterday.

21
00:02:41,310 --> 00:02:43,310
She wasn't feeling well last night,

22
00:02:43,910 --> 00:02:44,870
and today

23
00:02:45,400 --> 00:02:46,930
she couldn't get out of bed.

24
00:02:47,430 --> 00:02:49,030
Did you send for a physician?

25
00:02:49,190 --> 00:02:50,280
Yes.

26
00:02:51,000 --> 00:02:52,260
It's nothing serious.

27
00:02:53,560 --> 00:02:55,560
She's just overwhelmed with grief.

28
00:02:58,240 --> 00:02:59,900
When will the funeral be held?

29
00:03:01,590 --> 00:03:02,710
Not yet.

30
00:03:03,030 --> 00:03:04,430
My mother's last wish was

31
00:03:05,080 --> 00:03:08,340
to be buried in the Ji family
ancestral ground in Tongzhou.

32
00:03:09,560 --> 00:03:10,490
Did the Gu family

33
00:03:10,840 --> 00:03:11,870
agree to that?

34
00:03:13,800 --> 00:03:15,460
That's not for them to decide.

35
00:03:17,870 --> 00:03:19,870
I've sent people to look for Yuping.

36
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:21,460
There should be news soon.

37
00:03:22,460 --> 00:03:23,860
Thank you, Third Master.

38
00:03:53,590 --> 00:03:54,910
If you hadn't brought Yuping here,

39
00:03:54,910 --> 00:03:56,510
Mother would still be alive!

40
00:03:57,630 --> 00:03:58,560
It's my fault too

41
00:03:59,120 --> 00:04:00,780
for believing your nonsense!

42
00:04:01,630 --> 00:04:02,680
You said you were craving

43
00:04:02,680 --> 00:04:04,480
Li's sugar-roasted chestnuts,

44
00:04:05,710 --> 00:04:06,750
because I told you

45
00:04:06,750 --> 00:04:07,750
Yuping's family

46
00:04:07,750 --> 00:04:09,310
owned that shop, right?

47
00:04:09,750 --> 00:04:11,000
So you knew that finding Li's shop

48
00:04:11,000 --> 00:04:13,060
would lead you to Yuping, didn't you?

49
00:04:14,400 --> 00:04:15,840
I did want to find Yuping,

50
00:04:16,480 --> 00:04:17,750
but I never thought

51
00:04:19,120 --> 00:04:20,850
Mother would take her own life.

52
00:04:35,600 --> 00:04:36,800
I see.

53
00:04:38,510 --> 00:04:40,130
No wonder you've been

54
00:04:40,360 --> 00:04:41,920
acting so strangely lately.

55
00:04:41,920 --> 00:04:42,600
So it was you

56
00:04:42,600 --> 00:04:44,000
who helped find Yuping.

57
00:04:44,630 --> 00:04:45,630
Zhao!

58
00:04:46,240 --> 00:04:47,560
I was wrong. I didn't know

59
00:04:47,560 --> 00:04:49,220
things would end up like this.

60
00:04:49,270 --> 00:04:50,190
I deserve to die.

61
00:04:50,190 --> 00:04:51,900
I really do!

62
00:04:52,270 --> 00:04:54,070
This has nothing to do with Rong.

63
00:04:54,830 --> 00:04:55,870
I lied to him.

64
00:04:56,270 --> 00:04:57,120
He had no idea

65
00:04:57,120 --> 00:04:58,560
I was using him to get information.

66
00:04:58,560 --> 00:05:00,220
If you want to punish someone,

67
00:05:00,480 --> 00:05:02,220
just come at me.

68
00:05:02,750 --> 00:05:04,880
Stop putting on that act in front of me.

69
00:05:05,120 --> 00:05:06,000
I always treated you

70
00:05:06,000 --> 00:05:07,200
as my closest family,

71
00:05:07,950 --> 00:05:09,120
yet you used me

72
00:05:09,120 --> 00:05:10,520
and got my mother killed!

73
00:05:11,560 --> 00:05:12,310
Rong.

74
00:05:12,950 --> 00:05:14,190
I'm your sister, so listen to me.

75
00:05:14,190 --> 00:05:15,720
What kind of sister are you?

76
00:05:16,510 --> 00:05:18,560
I don't want a sister like you anymore!

77
00:05:18,560 --> 00:05:19,430
Rong.

78
00:05:21,770 --> 00:05:24,070
I've decided to go
to the Shuntian Prefecture

79
00:05:24,070 --> 00:05:26,930
and accuse Gu Dezhao
of driving his wife to suicide.

80
00:05:31,630 --> 00:05:32,960
Have you lost your mind?

81
00:05:34,240 --> 00:05:35,720
He's the real culprit.

82
00:05:36,430 --> 00:05:37,680
But do you realize

83
00:05:38,159 --> 00:05:39,870
accusing your own father is a felony?

84
00:05:39,870 --> 00:05:41,750
Before the case begins,
you'll take 40 strokes of the cane first!

85
00:05:41,750 --> 00:05:42,600
So what?

86
00:05:45,560 --> 00:05:46,310
I have to

87
00:05:46,310 --> 00:05:47,510
seek justice for her.

88
00:05:49,630 --> 00:05:50,560
Even if you are not afraid

89
00:05:50,560 --> 00:05:51,800
of physical pain,

90
00:05:52,430 --> 00:05:53,480
once you do this,

91
00:05:54,190 --> 00:05:55,240
the Gu family's reputation

92
00:05:55,240 --> 00:05:56,570
will be totally ruined.

93
00:05:56,750 --> 00:05:58,720
Don't you want to get married someday?

94
00:05:58,720 --> 00:06:00,380
And what about Rong's future?

95
00:06:00,830 --> 00:06:01,600
Don't you care about

96
00:06:01,600 --> 00:06:02,860
Rong's future either?

97
00:06:06,270 --> 00:06:08,200
I'm not here to discuss it with you.

98
00:06:09,390 --> 00:06:10,120
I just came here

99
00:06:10,120 --> 00:06:11,160
to inform you.

100
00:06:16,870 --> 00:06:17,670
Let me sue him!

101
00:06:20,450 --> 00:06:21,390
I'm also responsible for Mother's death,

102
00:06:21,390 --> 00:06:23,050
and I deserve no forgiveness.

103
00:06:24,680 --> 00:06:26,630
Let me file the accusation instead.

104
00:06:26,630 --> 00:06:28,430
I'll take the 40 strokes myself.

105
00:06:30,070 --> 00:06:30,830
Fine.

106
00:06:32,720 --> 00:06:34,720
Once I finish writing the petition,

107
00:06:35,560 --> 00:06:37,159
I'll have you sign it with me.

108
00:06:52,240 --> 00:06:53,630
Crazy.

109
00:06:54,560 --> 00:06:56,430
They're all crazy.

110
00:07:19,040 --> 00:07:19,720
My Lady.

111
00:07:22,070 --> 00:07:23,310
I was just about to look for you.

112
00:07:23,310 --> 00:07:24,660
A letter from Guard Chen says

113
00:07:24,660 --> 00:07:25,920
Yuping has been found.

114
00:07:43,560 --> 00:07:44,800
You are...

115
00:07:46,720 --> 00:07:47,680
Miss Gu.

116
00:07:48,810 --> 00:07:49,710
Miss Gu!

117
00:07:49,770 --> 00:07:50,820
I was wrong.

118
00:07:50,870 --> 00:07:52,170
I'm sorry.

119
00:07:52,270 --> 00:07:53,720
I'm truly sorry.

120
00:07:53,830 --> 00:07:54,520
Back then,

121
00:07:54,920 --> 00:07:56,920
I was the one who swapped
the labor-inducing medicine

122
00:07:56,920 --> 00:07:58,420
that Yun drank.

123
00:07:58,510 --> 00:08:00,160
It had nothing to do with Madam Ji Han.

124
00:08:00,160 --> 00:08:02,000
I'm willing to confess
and take the punishment.

125
00:08:02,000 --> 00:08:03,210
I only beg you

126
00:08:03,240 --> 00:08:03,920
to spare my

127
00:08:03,920 --> 00:08:05,270
two children.

128
00:08:05,360 --> 00:08:06,190
Please.

129
00:08:06,270 --> 00:08:07,260
Please.

130
00:08:07,390 --> 00:08:08,780
I beg you.

131
00:08:09,560 --> 00:08:11,120
Why did you harm Yun Xiang?

132
00:08:17,390 --> 00:08:18,190
Years ago,

133
00:08:19,040 --> 00:08:20,920
Madam Ji Han wanted to promote someone

134
00:08:20,920 --> 00:08:22,840
to divide Master's affection away
from Madam Song,

135
00:08:22,840 --> 00:08:23,520
so I...

136
00:08:23,830 --> 00:08:26,030
harbored thoughts I never should have,

137
00:08:26,510 --> 00:08:27,800
and even begged Madam to choose me.

138
00:08:27,800 --> 00:08:28,600
But Madam Ji Han

139
00:08:28,600 --> 00:08:29,930
chose Yun Xiang instead

140
00:08:30,000 --> 00:08:31,730
and assigned me to serve her.

141
00:08:33,150 --> 00:08:34,270
Yun Xiang relied

142
00:08:34,270 --> 00:08:35,200
on her pregnancy

143
00:08:35,240 --> 00:08:36,150
to boss me around

144
00:08:36,150 --> 00:08:37,150
every single day.

145
00:08:37,240 --> 00:08:39,700
I couldn't bear the humiliation anymore...

146
00:08:40,000 --> 00:08:41,299
so I gave her

147
00:08:41,720 --> 00:08:42,870
the labor-inducing soup

148
00:08:42,870 --> 00:08:45,210
and told her it could prevent miscarriage.

149
00:08:45,210 --> 00:08:47,340
Just because Madam chose Yun Xiang,

150
00:08:47,750 --> 00:08:48,790
instead of you,

151
00:08:50,430 --> 00:08:52,220
and you decided to harm her?

152
00:08:53,510 --> 00:08:54,400
I'm guilty!

153
00:08:54,420 --> 00:08:56,720
I deserve death.

154
00:08:57,200 --> 00:08:58,670
I have no idea

155
00:08:58,720 --> 00:09:00,320
what came over me at the time.

156
00:09:00,960 --> 00:09:02,600
It was as if I were possessed.

157
00:09:03,600 --> 00:09:04,580
So...

158
00:09:04,790 --> 00:09:06,790
you had feelings for Master as well?

159
00:09:07,080 --> 00:09:08,810
No, no, no. It wasn't like that.

160
00:09:09,390 --> 00:09:10,630
I didn't understand

161
00:09:10,670 --> 00:09:12,380
what love even was.

162
00:09:12,750 --> 00:09:13,690
At the time,

163
00:09:13,790 --> 00:09:16,240
I simply thought
that as Madam's dowry maid,

164
00:09:16,240 --> 00:09:17,360
I was meant

165
00:09:17,360 --> 00:09:19,090
to become Master's concubine.

166
00:09:19,340 --> 00:09:20,200
Unexpectedly,

167
00:09:20,320 --> 00:09:22,050
Madam chose Yun Xiang instead,

168
00:09:22,200 --> 00:09:24,460
and said my temperament was unsuitable.

169
00:09:24,670 --> 00:09:25,540
She told me

170
00:09:25,630 --> 00:09:26,670
to choose a servant
from the outer courtyard

171
00:09:26,670 --> 00:09:27,800
and get married off.

172
00:09:28,180 --> 00:09:29,980
I didn't want to marry a servant.

173
00:09:31,030 --> 00:09:32,200
So I...

174
00:09:32,750 --> 00:09:34,000
You committed murder,

175
00:09:34,000 --> 00:09:36,320
yet you were only expelled
from the mansion—

176
00:09:36,320 --> 00:09:38,120
you should consider yourself lucky.

177
00:09:38,120 --> 00:09:39,240
Then why did you suddenly come back

178
00:09:39,240 --> 00:09:40,360
to frame Mrs. Gu?

179
00:09:41,240 --> 00:09:42,670
I didn't come back

180
00:09:42,670 --> 00:09:44,200
to frame her on purpose.

181
00:09:44,910 --> 00:09:46,440
Miss Lan and Madam Song

182
00:09:46,440 --> 00:09:47,500
came to question me

183
00:09:47,550 --> 00:09:48,960
about the incident from years ago.

184
00:09:48,960 --> 00:09:49,780
They asked

185
00:09:49,840 --> 00:09:52,170
whether Madam had switched the medicine.

186
00:09:53,320 --> 00:09:55,050
I couldn't admit

187
00:09:55,240 --> 00:09:56,970
that it was my doing,

188
00:09:57,200 --> 00:09:59,000
so I went along with their story.

189
00:09:59,550 --> 00:10:01,210
Then Madam Song promised me

190
00:10:01,790 --> 00:10:02,550
a reward of two hundred taels of silver,

191
00:10:02,550 --> 00:10:04,750
if I was willing to testify against Madam

192
00:10:04,750 --> 00:10:06,800
in front of Master.

193
00:10:07,670 --> 00:10:09,310
I couldn't resist the money,

194
00:10:09,910 --> 00:10:10,440
so I...

195
00:10:11,840 --> 00:10:12,850
I'm so sorry.

196
00:10:13,120 --> 00:10:15,480
I made a terrible mistake.

197
00:10:33,030 --> 00:10:34,030
How would you like

198
00:10:35,200 --> 00:10:36,460
to handle this matter?

199
00:10:41,600 --> 00:10:42,750
Could you give me Yuping's

200
00:10:42,750 --> 00:10:43,950
wrriten confession?

201
00:10:43,960 --> 00:10:45,890
I was going to give it to you anyway.

202
00:10:46,080 --> 00:10:47,680
What do you want to do with it?

203
00:10:49,200 --> 00:10:51,530
If I take this to the Shuntian Prefecture,

204
00:10:51,750 --> 00:10:53,750
will he be stripped of his position?

205
00:10:54,910 --> 00:10:56,840
I can have him stripped of his post.

206
00:10:57,390 --> 00:10:59,120
Then let's expose everything.

207
00:11:00,390 --> 00:11:01,120
I was already planning

208
00:11:01,120 --> 00:11:02,650
to take him to court anyway.

209
00:11:03,750 --> 00:11:06,150
Are you sure you want
to sue your own father?

210
00:11:08,630 --> 00:11:10,290
Do you think I've lost my mind?

211
00:11:11,790 --> 00:11:12,550
I know

212
00:11:14,600 --> 00:11:15,390
that my mother

213
00:11:15,390 --> 00:11:17,450
wasn't directly killed by my father.

214
00:11:17,870 --> 00:11:19,080
And I also know

215
00:11:19,630 --> 00:11:21,760
the odds of winning this case
are slim.

216
00:11:23,270 --> 00:11:24,800
But I never expected to win.

217
00:11:27,480 --> 00:11:28,670
I just want to

218
00:11:29,630 --> 00:11:30,840
ruin his reputation.

219
00:11:31,850 --> 00:11:33,160
But do you realize

220
00:11:33,790 --> 00:11:36,360
that if a child accuses their own father,
regardless of right or wrong,

221
00:11:36,360 --> 00:11:38,440
they must first
endure 40 strokes of the cane?

222
00:11:38,440 --> 00:11:39,100
I know.

223
00:11:41,080 --> 00:11:42,540
But I'm willing to take it.

224
00:11:46,120 --> 00:11:47,910
My mother was driven to this end

225
00:11:48,510 --> 00:11:49,870
all because of him.

226
00:11:51,000 --> 00:11:53,000
I refuse to let him walk away with it.

227
00:11:58,360 --> 00:11:58,910
Fine.

228
00:12:19,390 --> 00:12:20,190
What's wrong?

229
00:12:20,550 --> 00:12:22,200
You helped Miss Gu today,

230
00:12:22,840 --> 00:12:24,550
but you still seem troubled.

231
00:12:28,020 --> 00:12:30,080
She wants to go to the Shuntian Prefecture

232
00:12:30,080 --> 00:12:31,440
to accuse Gu Dezhao.

233
00:12:32,510 --> 00:12:33,640
And you agreed to it?

234
00:12:35,360 --> 00:12:35,890
I mean...

235
00:12:36,930 --> 00:12:38,100
for a child to accuse their own father,

236
00:12:38,100 --> 00:12:39,510
it's a serious violation of filial piety!

237
00:12:39,510 --> 00:12:40,550
She can't possibly win.

238
00:12:40,550 --> 00:12:42,550
Why are you letting her have her way?

239
00:12:43,320 --> 00:12:44,600
She is filled with anger,

240
00:12:44,600 --> 00:12:46,400
and that anger must be released.

241
00:12:46,720 --> 00:12:47,480
Otherwise,

242
00:12:47,870 --> 00:12:49,000
it will consume her.

243
00:12:50,510 --> 00:12:52,840
But she'll have
to endure 40 strokes of the cane.

244
00:12:52,840 --> 00:12:54,970
Can you bear to watch Miss Gu be beaten?

245
00:13:00,030 --> 00:13:00,960
That is exactly

246
00:13:01,240 --> 00:13:02,510
why I need your help.

247
00:13:04,290 --> 00:13:06,230
[Case Precedents]

248
00:13:04,750 --> 00:13:06,080
In the 17th year of Jingning,

249
00:13:06,080 --> 00:13:08,240
a scholar from Zhending Prefecture
named Zhu Zhengrong

250
00:13:08,240 --> 00:13:09,550
accsued his own father—

251
00:13:09,550 --> 00:13:12,600
because his father was later found guilty
of unforgivable crimes,

252
00:13:12,600 --> 00:13:14,320
Zhu Zhengrong was exempted
from the strokes of the cane.

253
00:13:14,320 --> 00:13:15,370
Find a few more

254
00:13:15,440 --> 00:13:16,640
similar cases for me.

255
00:13:16,840 --> 00:13:18,370
I'll bring them to Yao Ping.

256
00:13:21,250 --> 00:13:22,650
Are you planning

257
00:13:22,840 --> 00:13:24,120
to change the law for this?

258
00:13:24,120 --> 00:13:25,920
The law is based on human nature.

259
00:13:25,960 --> 00:13:27,550
Besides, Gu Dezhao is guilty

260
00:13:27,550 --> 00:13:28,510
to begin with.

261
00:13:29,270 --> 00:13:29,870
By the way.

262
00:13:30,320 --> 00:13:31,710
Find a few censors

263
00:13:32,080 --> 00:13:34,130
to impeach Gu Dezhao—
charge him with favoring his concubine

264
00:13:34,130 --> 00:13:35,790
and driving his wife to death.

265
00:13:35,840 --> 00:13:37,700
Let's shape the narrative first.

266
00:13:38,440 --> 00:13:40,000
Since she insists on accusing him,

267
00:13:40,000 --> 00:13:40,930
I should at least

268
00:13:41,300 --> 00:13:42,890
pave the way for her.

269
00:13:43,980 --> 00:13:48,870
[Immersed in the Classics and History]

270
00:13:45,670 --> 00:13:46,720
But shouldn't you

271
00:13:46,720 --> 00:13:48,450
be dissuading Miss Gu instead?

272
00:13:49,630 --> 00:13:51,090
You wouldn't understand.

273
00:13:53,200 --> 00:13:54,000
Third Master.

274
00:13:54,960 --> 00:13:56,050
A message has just arrived.

275
00:13:56,050 --> 00:13:59,240
[Immersed in the Classics and History]

276
00:14:15,580 --> 00:14:18,820
[Wenyuan Pavilion]

277
00:14:23,750 --> 00:14:24,950
Greetings, Lord Fan.

278
00:14:39,910 --> 00:14:41,390
That old fool Fan Chuan

279
00:14:41,510 --> 00:14:43,390
has always been so stubborn!

280
00:14:44,630 --> 00:14:45,510
He refuses to acknowledge

281
00:14:45,510 --> 00:14:46,790
the advantages of sea transport,

282
00:14:46,790 --> 00:14:49,320
and insists
on opening canal routes instead.

283
00:14:49,630 --> 00:14:51,950
Today, the Imperial Board of Astronomy

284
00:14:52,030 --> 00:14:53,220
said that this year's climate

285
00:14:53,220 --> 00:14:54,790
is different from previous years—

286
00:14:54,790 --> 00:14:57,220
the summer floods may arrive early.

287
00:14:57,390 --> 00:14:59,190
If the summer flood comes early,

288
00:14:59,440 --> 00:15:00,270
won't the banks of the Yellow River

289
00:15:00,270 --> 00:15:02,000
and Huai River overflow again?

290
00:15:02,200 --> 00:15:04,320
The imperial court must prepare
for disaster relief immediately.

291
00:15:04,320 --> 00:15:06,910
Disaster relief is actually
a secondary concern.

292
00:15:06,910 --> 00:15:07,640
Come with me.

293
00:15:07,910 --> 00:15:09,240
Let me explain it to you.

294
00:15:10,510 --> 00:15:12,640
Once the Yellow River bursts its banks

295
00:15:13,320 --> 00:15:14,600
and the water changes its course,

296
00:15:14,490 --> 00:15:16,480
[Pei County] [Xuzhou]

297
00:15:14,840 --> 00:15:15,550
the water levels in Pei County,

298
00:15:15,550 --> 00:15:16,440
Xuzhou,

299
00:15:16,510 --> 00:15:17,930
[Suqian] [Huai'an]

300
00:15:16,630 --> 00:15:18,080
Suqian, and Huai'an

301
00:15:18,540 --> 00:15:21,040
will inevitably drop.

302
00:15:21,120 --> 00:15:23,030
By then, the silting in the watercourse

303
00:15:23,030 --> 00:15:24,320
will only become even worse.

304
00:15:24,320 --> 00:15:25,180
In other words,

305
00:15:26,320 --> 00:15:27,480
forget this year—

306
00:15:27,570 --> 00:15:29,500
even next year and the year after,

307
00:15:30,080 --> 00:15:32,480
the canal routes just won't recover.

308
00:15:33,030 --> 00:15:34,270
The moment Fan Chuan hears

309
00:15:34,270 --> 00:15:35,360
that the canal routes cannot recover,

310
00:15:35,360 --> 00:15:36,720
he will have no reason left

311
00:15:36,720 --> 00:15:38,670
to oppose sea transport.

312
00:15:39,380 --> 00:15:40,310
Wouldn't you say

313
00:15:40,320 --> 00:15:42,120
God is helping me?

314
00:15:52,080 --> 00:15:53,810
What do you want to see me about?

315
00:15:54,390 --> 00:15:55,720
Mentor, do you remember

316
00:15:56,320 --> 00:15:57,750
when I was attacked in Tongzhou,

317
00:15:57,750 --> 00:15:58,750
I mentioned that

318
00:15:59,510 --> 00:16:00,510
Prince Ruichang's heir

319
00:16:00,510 --> 00:16:03,320
had been selling
military weapons to the commoners.

320
00:16:03,320 --> 00:16:05,320
I followed this lead and discovered

321
00:16:05,390 --> 00:16:07,160
that recently a shipment of weapons

322
00:16:07,160 --> 00:16:08,640
bypassed the
Ministry of War's allocation process

323
00:16:08,640 --> 00:16:10,970
and was smuggled out through Ninghaiwei.

324
00:16:11,000 --> 00:16:11,840
It seems

325
00:16:12,330 --> 00:16:14,990
they're being transported back
to the capital.

326
00:16:16,480 --> 00:16:17,870
You're thinking...

327
00:16:18,200 --> 00:16:18,850
I think

328
00:16:19,360 --> 00:16:20,400
this matter is still

329
00:16:20,400 --> 00:16:22,100
related to Prince Ruichang.

330
00:16:22,600 --> 00:16:23,960
I'd like to follow the trail,

331
00:16:23,960 --> 00:16:26,160
let them in, and catch them red-handed.

332
00:16:27,090 --> 00:16:29,600
You may play along,

333
00:16:30,240 --> 00:16:31,480
but you can't actually

334
00:16:31,480 --> 00:16:32,750
let them into the capital.

335
00:16:32,750 --> 00:16:33,550
The capital

336
00:16:34,030 --> 00:16:35,230
cannot be put at risk.

337
00:16:37,030 --> 00:16:39,080
Then we should lure them to Tongzhou.

338
00:16:39,080 --> 00:16:40,780
The weapons are large.

339
00:16:41,080 --> 00:16:41,990
If they travel by land,

340
00:16:41,990 --> 00:16:43,240
they'll have to face many checkpoints,

341
00:16:43,240 --> 00:16:44,160
making it impossible to stay hidden.

342
00:16:44,160 --> 00:16:45,720
They must be taking the water route.

343
00:16:45,720 --> 00:16:47,010
And if they travel by water,

344
00:16:47,010 --> 00:16:49,470
they'll inevitably pass through Tongzhou.

345
00:16:49,870 --> 00:16:52,660
Then you should head to Tongzhou yourself.

346
00:16:52,750 --> 00:16:54,510
Come up with a proper excuse.

347
00:16:55,550 --> 00:16:57,550
My ancestral home is in Tongzhou.

348
00:16:58,030 --> 00:17:01,960
I was just thinking of returning there
to pay respects to my ancestors.

349
00:17:03,840 --> 00:17:04,640
Third Master,

350
00:17:05,030 --> 00:17:06,750
all the legal precedents of children

351
00:17:06,750 --> 00:17:09,150
accusing their fathers and being exempted

352
00:17:09,640 --> 00:17:11,440
from punishment are right here.

353
00:17:13,680 --> 00:17:14,960
Go to Shandong again.

354
00:17:15,240 --> 00:17:16,500
Deliver this letter to

355
00:17:16,550 --> 00:17:18,920
Pan Yuncheng
of the River Conservancy Office.

356
00:17:18,920 --> 00:17:20,849
Why reach out to him all of a sudden?

357
00:17:21,440 --> 00:17:23,400
The summer flood will be early this year.

358
00:17:23,400 --> 00:17:23,920
But

359
00:17:24,270 --> 00:17:26,109
the court will likely be unable to do much

360
00:17:26,109 --> 00:17:28,710
regarding river repairs
and disaster relief.

361
00:17:28,830 --> 00:17:29,510
Why?

362
00:17:30,110 --> 00:17:31,590
Isn't it true
that after the land tax reform,

363
00:17:31,590 --> 00:17:32,730
the Ministry of Revenue collected

364
00:17:32,730 --> 00:17:34,260
way more silver than usual?

365
00:17:34,590 --> 00:17:36,720
Is it because of the sea route project?

366
00:17:39,440 --> 00:17:41,240
Those are two separate matters.

367
00:17:41,790 --> 00:17:43,350
Surely no one would deliberately
neglect river repairs

368
00:17:43,350 --> 00:17:45,750
just to push forward sea transport, right?

369
00:17:47,070 --> 00:17:48,930
What did the Grand Secretary say?

370
00:17:53,220 --> 00:17:55,350
I just came from the Wenyuan Pavilion.

371
00:17:59,450 --> 00:18:00,750
I can't bypass my mentor

372
00:18:00,750 --> 00:18:03,030
and make a direct request
to Ministry of Revenue.

373
00:18:03,030 --> 00:18:05,160
Lord Pan and I
have worked together for many years.

374
00:18:05,160 --> 00:18:05,960
Tell him

375
00:18:06,720 --> 00:18:07,650
to prepare well.

376
00:18:08,750 --> 00:18:09,960
He'll know what to do.

377
00:18:14,070 --> 00:18:15,400
How did it come to this?

378
00:18:18,480 --> 00:18:19,430
Early tomorrow morning,

379
00:18:19,430 --> 00:18:21,110
you will escort the coffin
back to Tongzhou—

380
00:18:21,110 --> 00:18:22,370
on foot the entire way.

381
00:18:22,590 --> 00:18:23,920
How can you not eat more?

382
00:18:38,160 --> 00:18:39,290
That's more like it.

383
00:18:40,590 --> 00:18:41,200
Tomorrow morning,

384
00:18:41,200 --> 00:18:42,860
I will come check on you again.

385
00:18:47,350 --> 00:18:48,160
Yao.

386
00:18:57,780 --> 00:18:59,080
I heard from Rong

387
00:19:00,680 --> 00:19:02,340
that before Aunt passed away,

388
00:19:02,480 --> 00:19:04,340
she begged you to call her Mother.

389
00:19:05,400 --> 00:19:06,600
But you didn't say it.

390
00:19:08,070 --> 00:19:09,360
Now that she's gone,

391
00:19:10,440 --> 00:19:12,070
you must regret it deeply.

392
00:19:13,750 --> 00:19:14,920
But actually,

393
00:19:15,480 --> 00:19:17,210
you did call her Mother before.

394
00:19:18,480 --> 00:19:19,480
Not just Mother,

395
00:19:20,480 --> 00:19:21,810
you even called her Mom.

396
00:19:23,640 --> 00:19:24,970
Before you turned four,

397
00:19:25,720 --> 00:19:26,590
Aunt would return

398
00:19:26,590 --> 00:19:28,590
to Tongzhou to visit you every year.

399
00:19:30,070 --> 00:19:31,000
And every time,

400
00:19:31,440 --> 00:19:33,300
you would run to her from far away,

401
00:19:34,110 --> 00:19:35,160
calling her Mom,

402
00:19:36,030 --> 00:19:38,090
and throwing yourself into her arms.

403
00:19:38,750 --> 00:19:39,640
Then again,

404
00:19:40,790 --> 00:19:42,790
even if you never called her Mother—

405
00:19:44,000 --> 00:19:45,200
does that really mean

406
00:19:45,720 --> 00:19:47,920
you never thought of her as your mother?

407
00:19:50,350 --> 00:19:51,390
I don't think so.

408
00:19:52,240 --> 00:19:53,700
Because if that were true,

409
00:19:54,330 --> 00:19:55,930
why would you be this sad now?

410
00:20:03,590 --> 00:20:05,790
I'm not very good at comforting people,

411
00:20:05,890 --> 00:20:07,420
but I want to say this to you.

412
00:20:07,450 --> 00:20:08,510
It's okay to be sad.

413
00:20:09,160 --> 00:20:10,820
It's okay to cry if you need to.

414
00:20:12,380 --> 00:20:13,030
But don't

415
00:20:13,030 --> 00:20:14,680
let grief ruin your health.

416
00:20:15,350 --> 00:20:15,920
More importantly,

417
00:20:15,920 --> 00:20:17,510
don't hurt yourself just to punish people

418
00:20:17,510 --> 00:20:18,640
who aren't worth it.

419
00:20:19,270 --> 00:20:21,470
Because you are not alone in this world.

420
00:20:22,110 --> 00:20:23,570
Think about Grandmother.

421
00:20:24,110 --> 00:20:25,110
Think about Rong.

422
00:20:29,110 --> 00:20:30,170
And think about me.

423
00:20:44,070 --> 00:20:45,960
There are already more than ten memorials

424
00:20:45,960 --> 00:20:48,430
impeaching you for favoring your concubine

425
00:20:48,510 --> 00:20:50,640
and driving your lawful wife to death.

426
00:20:51,090 --> 00:20:53,220
Some of the more aggressive officials

427
00:20:53,440 --> 00:20:55,200
are even demanding
that you be stripped of your post

428
00:20:55,200 --> 00:20:56,530
and brought to justice.

429
00:20:56,610 --> 00:21:01,280
[Misty Waves in Serenity]

430
00:20:59,750 --> 00:21:01,160
I'm here to let you know

431
00:21:01,790 --> 00:21:02,590
and give you time

432
00:21:02,590 --> 00:21:03,790
to prepare yourself.

433
00:21:04,550 --> 00:21:05,370
For now,

434
00:21:05,440 --> 00:21:07,440
things haven't gotten that bad yet.

435
00:21:08,200 --> 00:21:09,960
But once those censors

436
00:21:09,960 --> 00:21:11,820
get their hands on hard evidence,

437
00:21:12,240 --> 00:21:14,030
you'll truly be doomed.

438
00:21:17,590 --> 00:21:19,710
I plan to go to the Shuntian Prefecture

439
00:21:19,710 --> 00:21:22,310
and accuse Gu Dezhao
of driving his wife to suicide.

440
00:21:22,310 --> 00:21:24,240
I'm not here to discuss it with you.

441
00:21:26,550 --> 00:21:27,200
I just came over

442
00:21:27,200 --> 00:21:28,400
to inform you.

443
00:21:34,310 --> 00:21:35,200
I'm finished.

444
00:21:46,110 --> 00:21:47,570
Do you also think

445
00:21:48,310 --> 00:21:49,640
I shouldn't sue Master?

446
00:21:52,000 --> 00:21:52,470
I...

447
00:21:53,550 --> 00:21:54,590
I just think

448
00:21:54,680 --> 00:21:56,160
Master deserves to be punished.

449
00:21:56,160 --> 00:21:57,440
But suing him

450
00:21:57,680 --> 00:21:59,430
at the cost of your reputation,

451
00:21:59,550 --> 00:22:00,750
Rong's future,

452
00:22:01,030 --> 00:22:02,640
and enduring that 40 strokes of the cane—

453
00:22:02,640 --> 00:22:03,500
I just think...

454
00:22:04,640 --> 00:22:05,640
it's not worth it.

455
00:22:14,480 --> 00:22:15,720
My future

456
00:22:16,590 --> 00:22:18,160
is all ruined!

457
00:22:42,830 --> 00:22:43,440
My Lady.

458
00:23:38,660 --> 00:23:39,410
Master.

459
00:24:02,380 --> 00:24:05,720
[Written Confession]

460
00:24:09,050 --> 00:24:10,790
It's my fault.

461
00:24:12,270 --> 00:24:14,070
It's all my fault.

462
00:24:15,750 --> 00:24:17,890
I wrongly blamed Han.

463
00:24:20,020 --> 00:24:23,200
I caused Han's death.

464
00:24:24,880 --> 00:24:27,500
It's all my fault!

465
00:24:28,960 --> 00:24:31,290
I planned to go to the Shuntian Prefecture

466
00:24:31,550 --> 00:24:32,180
to sue you.

467
00:24:33,750 --> 00:24:34,700
Oh...

468
00:24:41,550 --> 00:24:42,750
I've changed my mind.

469
00:24:44,120 --> 00:24:45,520
I've thought it through.

470
00:24:47,590 --> 00:24:48,980
If I sue you,

471
00:24:49,570 --> 00:24:52,100
the worst you'll face is
a ruined reputation,

472
00:24:52,190 --> 00:24:53,790
a demotion,
or being stripped of your post.

473
00:24:53,790 --> 00:24:54,750
And you

474
00:24:56,160 --> 00:24:57,820
deserve much worse than this.

475
00:25:01,240 --> 00:25:02,030
Tell me,

476
00:25:04,550 --> 00:25:06,610
why did Madam Ji Han take her own life?

477
00:25:08,070 --> 00:25:09,790
She... she was

478
00:25:10,160 --> 00:25:11,720
too hard on herself.

479
00:25:13,340 --> 00:25:16,040
She fell ill from depression.

480
00:25:23,170 --> 00:25:24,570
She was trapped by you,

481
00:25:25,790 --> 00:25:27,530
trapped by this mansion—

482
00:25:27,800 --> 00:25:28,890
with no way out.

483
00:25:31,510 --> 00:25:32,440
I want you to suffer

484
00:25:32,440 --> 00:25:33,510
the same as she did.

485
00:25:35,340 --> 00:25:36,780
What do you want?

486
00:25:37,990 --> 00:25:39,590
I want three things from you.

487
00:25:41,570 --> 00:25:42,330
First,

488
00:25:42,790 --> 00:25:43,900
from now on,

489
00:25:44,030 --> 00:25:45,240
whether you remarry

490
00:25:45,240 --> 00:25:46,770
or take another concubine,

491
00:25:47,640 --> 00:25:49,110
you must have my approval.

492
00:25:50,200 --> 00:25:50,720
What?

493
00:25:50,720 --> 00:25:51,200
Second,

494
00:25:52,160 --> 00:25:53,820
you have no right to interfere

495
00:25:54,550 --> 00:25:55,950
in my marriage or Rong's.

496
00:25:57,350 --> 00:25:58,590
How is that even possible?

497
00:25:58,590 --> 00:25:59,200
Third...

498
00:25:59,960 --> 00:26:00,640
Qingpu.

499
00:26:04,000 --> 00:26:04,920
What is this?

500
00:26:08,990 --> 00:26:12,150
[Letter of Amicable Separation]

501
00:26:12,880 --> 00:26:15,140
This is a letter of amicable separation.

502
00:26:16,310 --> 00:26:18,620
You want me to divorce your mother?

503
00:26:18,850 --> 00:26:22,050
-Your mother is already gone.
-You can still divorce her.

504
00:26:22,640 --> 00:26:23,140
My mo-

505
00:26:30,440 --> 00:26:31,640
my mother's last wish

506
00:26:33,110 --> 00:26:35,640
was not to be buried
in the Gu family burial grounds,

507
00:26:35,640 --> 00:26:38,240
but to be buried
with the Ji family in Tongzhou.

508
00:26:45,310 --> 00:26:46,840
Sign this letter,

509
00:26:47,480 --> 00:26:50,010
and the two of you
will be completely severed.

510
00:26:50,750 --> 00:26:51,320
This...

511
00:26:51,900 --> 00:26:52,680
[Letter of Amicable Separation]

512
00:26:59,270 --> 00:27:00,240
Zhao,

513
00:27:02,350 --> 00:27:04,270
why must you do this?

514
00:27:05,030 --> 00:27:06,770
I know you resent me

515
00:27:06,960 --> 00:27:09,110
because of what happened to your mother.

516
00:27:09,110 --> 00:27:10,910
But your mother is already gone.

517
00:27:10,930 --> 00:27:12,960
Divorcing her now

518
00:27:13,030 --> 00:27:13,830
won't benefit you

519
00:27:13,830 --> 00:27:14,790
or Rong

520
00:27:14,790 --> 00:27:17,330
in any way.

521
00:27:17,590 --> 00:27:19,240
As for Rong and me,

522
00:27:20,830 --> 00:27:22,760
you don't need to concern about us.

523
00:27:22,960 --> 00:27:24,110
Just sign it.

524
00:27:27,880 --> 00:27:30,550
I'm still your biological father.

525
00:27:31,440 --> 00:27:34,630
Why must you force me this far?

526
00:27:45,030 --> 00:27:46,310
If you refuse to sign,

527
00:27:46,820 --> 00:27:48,180
I'll sue you.

528
00:27:50,200 --> 00:27:51,110
At worst,

529
00:27:52,100 --> 00:27:54,160
we'll drag each other down together.

530
00:27:57,030 --> 00:27:58,230
No, no, please don't.

531
00:28:00,350 --> 00:28:01,160
I'll sign it.

532
00:28:02,870 --> 00:28:04,380
I'll sign it.

533
00:28:16,920 --> 00:28:20,280
[Signed by: Gu Dezhao]

534
00:28:34,740 --> 00:28:37,470
[Memorial]

535
00:28:37,540 --> 00:28:44,680
[Blessings Passed Down for Generations]
[Memorial]

536
00:28:37,750 --> 00:28:41,550
Mother!

537
00:28:44,790 --> 00:28:47,630
[Spirit Tablet of the Beloved Mother, Ji Han Yuan Zhen]

538
00:28:50,790 --> 00:28:51,760
Yao,

539
00:28:51,780 --> 00:28:53,440
we are about to leave the town.

540
00:28:53,440 --> 00:28:54,970
You should head back first.

541
00:28:56,310 --> 00:28:57,960
Grandmother is still unwell.

542
00:28:57,960 --> 00:28:59,040
The shop business

543
00:28:59,110 --> 00:29:00,110
can't run itself.

544
00:29:00,960 --> 00:29:01,880
They all need you

545
00:29:01,880 --> 00:29:03,740
to go back and take care of things.

546
00:29:04,240 --> 00:29:06,270
But it's a bit chaotic outside these days.

547
00:29:06,270 --> 00:29:06,770
I...

548
00:29:08,580 --> 00:29:12,290
[Ye]

549
00:29:19,060 --> 00:29:22,200
[Ye]

550
00:29:26,570 --> 00:29:29,000
[Ye]

551
00:29:33,890 --> 00:29:35,810
[Divine Mission, Eternal Prosperity:
The Legacy of the Ji Family]

552
00:29:35,830 --> 00:29:37,880
[The Coffin of Ji Han, Virtuous
Eldest Daughter and Honored Matriarch]

553
00:29:39,030 --> 00:29:39,550
Get up.

554
00:29:42,070 --> 00:29:43,030
Why are you here?

555
00:29:43,510 --> 00:29:44,590
Why didn't you tell me

556
00:29:44,590 --> 00:29:46,390
you were returning to Tongzhou?

557
00:29:48,920 --> 00:29:51,780
Were you planning to leave
without saying goodbye?

558
00:29:52,510 --> 00:29:54,170
After all we've been through,

559
00:29:54,200 --> 00:29:56,060
couldn't you at least let me know?

560
00:30:00,480 --> 00:30:01,140
Never mind.

561
00:30:02,480 --> 00:30:03,550
These are my men.

562
00:30:04,160 --> 00:30:04,790
I'll have them

563
00:30:04,790 --> 00:30:06,720
escort you back to Tongzhou later.

564
00:30:07,270 --> 00:30:07,770
This...

565
00:30:08,160 --> 00:30:09,760
They are my personal guards.

566
00:30:09,880 --> 00:30:11,270
The Yellow River
and Huai River have flooded.

567
00:30:11,270 --> 00:30:12,790
The grain shipments can't get through,

568
00:30:12,790 --> 00:30:14,750
and many areas have suffered disasters.

569
00:30:14,750 --> 00:30:15,720
Lately, in the capital,

570
00:30:15,720 --> 00:30:17,590
the number of refugees
has visibly increased.

571
00:30:17,590 --> 00:30:18,830
With this many carriages

572
00:30:18,830 --> 00:30:19,830
and so few guards,

573
00:30:20,590 --> 00:30:22,190
you'll be an obvious target.

574
00:30:23,310 --> 00:30:24,710
With them escorting you,

575
00:30:25,270 --> 00:30:26,530
I'll feel more at ease.

576
00:30:27,720 --> 00:30:28,240
Okay.

577
00:30:29,200 --> 00:30:29,800
Thank you.

578
00:30:32,880 --> 00:30:33,440
Rong.

579
00:30:37,680 --> 00:30:39,140
Thank you, Your Highness.

580
00:30:40,030 --> 00:30:41,510
With your men accompanying her,

581
00:30:41,510 --> 00:30:43,040
I feel much more reassured.

582
00:30:43,240 --> 00:30:44,830
Together with our own guards

583
00:30:44,830 --> 00:30:45,920
escorting my sister
all the way to Tongzhou,

584
00:30:45,920 --> 00:30:47,790
I suppose it should be safe for her.

585
00:30:47,790 --> 00:30:49,920
Then I'll head back to Tongzhou first.

586
00:30:49,940 --> 00:30:51,230
I'll wait for you to come back.

587
00:30:51,230 --> 00:30:52,050
Yao,

588
00:30:52,270 --> 00:30:53,930
take more men with you as well.

589
00:30:54,110 --> 00:30:55,880
Please be careful on the road.

590
00:31:13,680 --> 00:31:14,480
Thank you.

591
00:31:15,510 --> 00:31:16,240
For what?

592
00:31:16,830 --> 00:31:17,880
This isn't a gift.

593
00:31:18,920 --> 00:31:21,780
Remember to give me
enough silver as a reward later.

594
00:31:28,310 --> 00:31:30,510
This is the kitten we rescued last time.

595
00:31:30,680 --> 00:31:32,280
It's grown this big already.

596
00:31:42,310 --> 00:31:43,910
Alright, alright, alright.

597
00:31:49,640 --> 00:31:51,400
Since Baopu likes you so much,

598
00:31:52,270 --> 00:31:52,920
I'll let you

599
00:31:52,920 --> 00:31:54,240
take care of it for a few days.

600
00:31:54,240 --> 00:31:54,750
Me?

601
00:31:58,000 --> 00:31:59,000
I guess it's fine.

602
00:31:59,480 --> 00:32:00,070
But

603
00:32:00,310 --> 00:32:01,790
I'm only looking after it temporarily.

604
00:32:01,790 --> 00:32:03,000
This cat is still yours.

605
00:32:03,000 --> 00:32:04,500
You're responsible for it.

606
00:32:04,500 --> 00:32:05,560
When you come back,

607
00:32:05,920 --> 00:32:07,250
you have to take it back.

608
00:32:07,790 --> 00:32:08,400
Got it?

609
00:32:11,970 --> 00:32:13,300
Remember what you said.

610
00:32:16,750 --> 00:32:17,550
The weather looks

611
00:32:17,550 --> 00:32:18,950
like it's getting worse.

612
00:32:19,110 --> 00:32:20,170
Hurry up and leave.

613
00:32:41,790 --> 00:32:42,790
She has a sharp tongue,

614
00:32:42,790 --> 00:32:43,790
but a soft heart.

615
00:32:44,400 --> 00:32:46,260
She's clearly suffering inside,

616
00:32:46,680 --> 00:32:49,340
but she insists
on pretending nothing is wrong.

617
00:32:52,200 --> 00:32:52,830
Forget it.

618
00:32:53,480 --> 00:32:54,610
Three years, right?

619
00:32:55,350 --> 00:32:57,210
In three years, I'll protect you.

620
00:32:57,710 --> 00:32:59,570
I won't let anyone bully you.

621
00:33:03,200 --> 00:33:04,000
Young Master?

622
00:33:04,790 --> 00:33:06,680
She's already long out of sight.

623
00:33:11,240 --> 00:33:12,570
Of course I can see that.

624
00:33:19,760 --> 00:33:22,700
[Luhe Coaching Inn]

625
00:33:24,270 --> 00:33:25,240
I told you

626
00:33:25,920 --> 00:33:27,640
to set out earlier,

627
00:33:28,590 --> 00:33:31,120
but you insisted
on leaving in the afternoon.

628
00:33:31,160 --> 00:33:32,270
And now look,

629
00:33:32,720 --> 00:33:34,850
you've been caught in this heavy rain.

630
00:33:36,550 --> 00:33:38,150
Mother, have some tea first.

631
00:33:38,400 --> 00:33:39,030
Calm down.

632
00:33:39,640 --> 00:33:40,640
Out of nowhere,

633
00:33:42,030 --> 00:33:44,960
you said you wanted
to pay respects to the ancestors.

634
00:33:46,400 --> 00:33:49,550
You didn't ask your brother
and sister-in-law to return,

635
00:33:49,550 --> 00:33:51,210
nor did you bring your sister.

636
00:33:51,880 --> 00:33:53,030
Who knows

637
00:33:53,310 --> 00:33:54,880
what you're really up to?

638
00:33:56,880 --> 00:33:57,720
Never mind.

639
00:33:59,200 --> 00:34:00,880
Since you said so,

640
00:34:01,510 --> 00:34:03,000
I'll just go along with it.

641
00:34:04,270 --> 00:34:06,410
I'll accompany you back to Tongzhou.

642
00:34:06,830 --> 00:34:08,150
You are so eloquent, Mother.

643
00:34:08,150 --> 00:34:09,949
I don't even know how to respond.

644
00:34:14,320 --> 00:34:15,360
I heard

645
00:34:15,670 --> 00:34:17,030
Zhao's mother

646
00:34:17,550 --> 00:34:20,550
was driven to death by Gu Dezhao.

647
00:34:22,000 --> 00:34:23,400
Is it true?

648
00:34:23,400 --> 00:34:24,760
Of course it's not true.

649
00:34:26,070 --> 00:34:28,550
Mrs. Gu passed away because
her long-term illness became terminal;

650
00:34:28,550 --> 00:34:30,409
no medicine could have saved her.

651
00:34:30,550 --> 00:34:31,920
Mother, given your friendship

652
00:34:31,920 --> 00:34:32,920
with Old Madam Ji,

653
00:34:33,110 --> 00:34:35,030
you shouldn't spread rumors like that.

654
00:34:35,030 --> 00:34:36,710
Oh, look at you!

655
00:34:37,400 --> 00:34:39,510
I was just chatting with you,

656
00:34:40,230 --> 00:34:42,030
and you started lecturing me.

657
00:34:43,920 --> 00:34:45,520
When you arrive in Tongzhou,

658
00:34:45,760 --> 00:34:47,820
you should visit the Ji family often—

659
00:34:47,920 --> 00:34:49,400
offer some comfort to Old Madam Ji

660
00:34:49,400 --> 00:34:50,210
and Miss Gu.

661
00:34:52,110 --> 00:34:53,550
Of course.

662
00:34:56,630 --> 00:34:57,190
Wait.

663
00:34:58,760 --> 00:34:59,670
Is Zhao

664
00:34:59,960 --> 00:35:01,190
going back to Tongzhou too?

665
00:35:01,190 --> 00:35:03,630
Mrs. Gu's last wish
was to be buried in Tongzhou.

666
00:35:03,630 --> 00:35:04,280
So

667
00:35:05,030 --> 00:35:07,090
Miss Gu is escorting the coffin home.

668
00:35:07,400 --> 00:35:09,550
Why didn't you tell me earlier?

669
00:35:09,590 --> 00:35:11,550
We could have traveled together.

670
00:35:14,360 --> 00:35:15,110
But...

671
00:35:16,070 --> 00:35:17,920
it's probably for the best
that I didn't know.

672
00:35:17,920 --> 00:35:19,320
It saves a lot of trouble.

673
00:35:20,320 --> 00:35:21,440
After all,

674
00:35:21,590 --> 00:35:23,320
she's traveling with a coffin,

675
00:35:23,800 --> 00:35:25,590
and at my age,

676
00:35:26,480 --> 00:35:28,400
I can't bear to see such things.

677
00:35:30,280 --> 00:35:31,080
Third Master,

678
00:35:31,320 --> 00:35:31,800
Madam.

679
00:35:33,110 --> 00:35:33,710
Is it here?

680
00:35:33,800 --> 00:35:34,150
Yes.

681
00:35:35,000 --> 00:35:36,030
Who's here?

682
00:35:38,480 --> 00:35:40,940
The Ji family's
funeral procession is here.

683
00:35:41,480 --> 00:35:42,000
Mother,

684
00:35:42,230 --> 00:35:43,490
I'll take my leave now.

685
00:35:44,590 --> 00:35:45,120
Let's go.

686
00:35:48,280 --> 00:35:48,680
You...

687
00:35:52,110 --> 00:35:52,910
It's raining.

688
00:35:54,920 --> 00:35:55,450
Hurry up.

689
00:35:57,360 --> 00:35:58,710
No matter how many rooms they have,

690
00:35:58,710 --> 00:35:59,840
we'll book them all.

691
00:36:00,920 --> 00:36:02,460
Then ask the people at the inn

692
00:36:02,460 --> 00:36:03,620
to clear out the woodshed

693
00:36:03,620 --> 00:36:05,400
so we can place the coffin there.

694
00:36:05,400 --> 00:36:06,600
If that doesn't work,

695
00:36:06,880 --> 00:36:08,540
we'll have to build a shelter.

696
00:36:10,320 --> 00:36:10,840
Right.

697
00:36:11,280 --> 00:36:13,510
And regarding the Marquis's ten guards,

698
00:36:13,510 --> 00:36:15,000
please let them know—whatever they need,

699
00:36:15,000 --> 00:36:16,590
they should feel free to ask.

700
00:36:16,590 --> 00:36:17,320
Understood.

701
00:36:18,150 --> 00:36:18,670
My Lady.

702
00:36:18,920 --> 00:36:20,180
It's the Third Master.

703
00:36:23,590 --> 00:36:24,390
Third Master.

704
00:36:28,190 --> 00:36:29,150
We came across

705
00:36:29,190 --> 00:36:31,070
the memorial shed
that Chen family made along the road.

706
00:36:31,070 --> 00:36:32,600
Thank you for your trouble.

707
00:36:33,270 --> 00:36:34,960
Our families have been close for years.

708
00:36:34,960 --> 00:36:36,690
There's no need to be so formal.

709
00:36:37,750 --> 00:36:39,280
Since the Old Madam's here,

710
00:36:39,510 --> 00:36:41,510
I should've gone to pay my respects.

711
00:36:42,190 --> 00:36:43,670
But since I'm in mourning,

712
00:36:44,880 --> 00:36:46,550
I was afraid it might not be appropriate.

713
00:36:46,550 --> 00:36:47,150
It's fine.

714
00:36:47,630 --> 00:36:49,070
My mother knows you're coming.

715
00:36:49,070 --> 00:36:50,760
She specifically asked me to tell you

716
00:36:50,760 --> 00:36:52,160
not to stand on ceremony,

717
00:36:52,480 --> 00:36:54,540
and you should take care of yourself.

718
00:37:00,630 --> 00:37:02,090
Greetings, Third Master.

719
00:37:04,630 --> 00:37:06,110
Many people are heading
to the capital recently.

720
00:37:06,110 --> 00:37:08,230
Only six rooms in the West Wing are left.

721
00:37:08,230 --> 00:37:10,090
I'm afraid it might not be enough.

722
00:37:11,280 --> 00:37:13,410
We'd rather have our people squeeze in

723
00:37:14,000 --> 00:37:15,920
than slight the Marquis's guards.

724
00:37:15,920 --> 00:37:16,650
Yes, My Lady.

725
00:37:18,440 --> 00:37:19,030
Guards?

726
00:37:20,630 --> 00:37:22,160
Ye Xian sent guards for you?

727
00:37:23,510 --> 00:37:24,070
Yes.

728
00:37:25,590 --> 00:37:26,710
He said it might

729
00:37:27,150 --> 00:37:28,350
not be safe on the way.

730
00:37:29,280 --> 00:37:30,480
How many guards are there?

731
00:37:30,480 --> 00:37:31,150
Ten.

732
00:37:35,030 --> 00:37:35,630
Chen Yi.

733
00:37:37,400 --> 00:37:38,460
Yes, Third Master.

734
00:37:38,480 --> 00:37:39,840
Tell our people

735
00:37:39,840 --> 00:37:41,100
to clear out some rooms

736
00:37:41,280 --> 00:37:42,880
enough for ten people to stay.

737
00:37:42,880 --> 00:37:43,610
Yes, Master.

738
00:37:45,110 --> 00:37:46,510
Thank you, Third Master.

739
00:37:46,550 --> 00:37:47,510
Thank you, Guard Chen.

740
00:37:47,510 --> 00:37:48,150
You're welcome.

741
00:37:48,150 --> 00:37:48,800
Follow me.

742
00:37:57,520 --> 00:38:00,030
[Inn]

743
00:38:08,190 --> 00:38:09,730
Hurry up.

744
00:38:09,880 --> 00:38:10,400
Yes, ma'am.

745
00:38:10,400 --> 00:38:11,060
Yes, ma'am.

746
00:38:11,360 --> 00:38:12,280
Get it up there.

747
00:38:13,150 --> 00:38:13,600
Okay.

748
00:38:14,440 --> 00:38:16,000
Hurry, over here too.

749
00:38:16,760 --> 00:38:17,420
Yes, ma'am.

750
00:38:20,960 --> 00:38:21,560
Over here.

751
00:38:21,630 --> 00:38:22,760
The rain is so heavy.

752
00:38:22,760 --> 00:38:24,820
Everyone, be careful not to get hurt.

753
00:38:25,000 --> 00:38:26,200
Don't worry, My Lady.

754
00:38:28,800 --> 00:38:29,880
Hurry, be careful.

755
00:38:31,030 --> 00:38:32,090
-Over here.
-Here.

756
00:39:23,190 --> 00:39:24,550
Go find something

757
00:39:25,000 --> 00:39:27,400
to put another two layers underneath this.

758
00:39:27,440 --> 00:39:28,700
I'll go find some wood.

759
00:40:27,190 --> 00:40:28,190
Still not asleep?

760
00:40:32,320 --> 00:40:33,520
I can't sleep either.

761
00:40:34,630 --> 00:40:35,590
I'm used to it.

762
00:40:36,400 --> 00:40:38,860
I can't fall asleep
before the second watch.

763
00:40:40,670 --> 00:40:41,440
Are you cold?

764
00:40:55,440 --> 00:40:57,240
I'm not going to sue him anymore.

765
00:41:03,280 --> 00:41:04,920
I've made so many mistakes.

766
00:41:07,030 --> 00:41:09,090
When I first returned to the capital,

767
00:41:11,030 --> 00:41:12,550
I never wanted anything

768
00:41:12,550 --> 00:41:13,920
to do with the Gu family.

769
00:41:15,440 --> 00:41:17,240
All I thought about was revenge.

770
00:41:20,550 --> 00:41:21,360
Sure enough,

771
00:41:24,280 --> 00:41:25,440
I quickly found

772
00:41:25,440 --> 00:41:26,880
Nanny Zhou's fault,

773
00:41:28,810 --> 00:41:30,480
and had her beaten.

774
00:41:31,360 --> 00:41:32,230
Later,

775
00:41:32,390 --> 00:41:34,660
at Lord Lin's birthday celebration...

776
00:41:36,550 --> 00:41:38,550
I humiliated my father in public.

777
00:41:40,620 --> 00:41:42,750
Alhough I was forced by circumstance,

778
00:41:44,190 --> 00:41:45,630
I also intended

779
00:41:46,230 --> 00:41:47,880
to make a fool of him.

780
00:41:51,550 --> 00:41:52,590
Later,

781
00:41:53,440 --> 00:41:56,240
when the Liu family came
with a marriage proposal,

782
00:41:56,760 --> 00:41:58,760
I found a way to reject them as well.

783
00:42:02,920 --> 00:42:05,000
Until I found rhubarb

784
00:42:05,150 --> 00:42:06,550
in my mother's medicine.

785
00:42:08,030 --> 00:42:09,070
I thought

786
00:42:10,280 --> 00:42:12,410
I still had everything under control.

787
00:42:13,440 --> 00:42:14,280
I thought

788
00:42:14,480 --> 00:42:16,420
things would always go my way.

789
00:42:18,070 --> 00:42:19,280
So I didn't hesitate

790
00:42:19,280 --> 00:42:21,070
to expose the truth.

791
00:42:21,880 --> 00:42:23,630
I claimed to investigate

792
00:42:25,760 --> 00:42:27,880
and cornered my opponent.

793
00:42:29,290 --> 00:42:32,150
I had nothing left to lose,
so I gambled everything.

794
00:42:38,960 --> 00:42:40,590
Then my mother died.

795
00:42:46,030 --> 00:42:48,430
These past few days, I've been thinking...

796
00:42:50,070 --> 00:42:51,400
if I hadn't been

797
00:42:52,550 --> 00:42:54,030
so impulsive back then,

798
00:42:56,190 --> 00:42:57,710
if I had just quietly

799
00:42:58,670 --> 00:43:00,480
treating my mother's illness,

800
00:43:02,440 --> 00:43:04,360
would she still be alive?

801
00:43:14,360 --> 00:43:15,760
It's all my fault.

802
00:43:25,110 --> 00:43:26,000
Is there

803
00:43:27,670 --> 00:43:29,070
a song you'd like to hear?

804
00:43:43,310 --> 00:43:46,830
[A Splendid Match]
